OL,3,CCarlisle not shortlisted for UK City
OL,4,Cof Culture as city misses out
OL,6,FCarlisle has not been shortlisted to
OL,7,Fbe the UK's City of Culture for 2029
OL,8,Fdespite registering an expression of
OL,9,Finterest to do so.
OL,11,FCumberland Council submitted their
OL,12,Finterest in the Cumbrian city being
OL,13,Fthe UK's City of Culture for 2029 but
OL,14,Fin a list published by the UK
OL,15,FGovernment the city has not made the
OL,16,Ffinal shortlist of nine.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
