PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773929472
OL,3,CCarlisle not shortlisted for UK City
OL,4,Cof Culture as city misses out
OL,6,FThe UK Government says that "winning
OL,7,Fthis title will have enormous benefits
OL,8,Ffor local communities, with previous
OL,9,Fhosts attracting millions of pounds in
OL,10,Fadditional investment and thousands of
OL,11,Fvisitors to their area, as well as
OL,12,Fgenerating new jobs."
OL,14,FWhat nine cities have been shortlisted?
OL,16,FEach of the nine shortlisted cities
OL,17,Fwill receive #60,000 to develop a full
OL,18,Fapplication.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
