OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773929472
OL,3,CCarlisle not shortlisted for UK City
OL,4,Cof Culture as city misses out
OL,6,FIn a statement the UK Government said:
OL,7,F"Today's announcement comes as over
OL,8,F230 towns have thrown their hat into
OL,9,Fthe ring to become the UK's first-ever
OL,10,FTown of Culture by registering their
OL,11,Finterest in bidding for that title.
OL,13,F"Many towns have also declared that
OL,14,Fthey will be submitting a bid, to
OL,15,Fhighlight their unique story and the
OL,16,Felements of their local culture and
OL,17,Fheritage that they would celebrate
OL,18,Fshould they be successful.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773929472
OL,3,CCarlisle not shortlisted for UK City
OL,4,Cof Culture as city misses out
OL,6,F"The competition is open to
OL,7,Fapplications from small, medium and
OL,8,Flarge towns for just under two more
OL,9,Fweeks, with the winner then tasked
OL,10,Fwith delivering a vibrant cultural
OL,11,Fprogramme in 2028.
OL,13,F"Both of these competitions are part
OL,14,Fof the Prime Minister's ambition to
OL,15,Frestore pride in every part of Britain.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1773929472
OL,3,CCarlisle not shortlisted for UK City
OL,4,Cof Culture as city misses out
OL,6,F"Throughout this year, both
OL,7,Fcompetitions will continue to shine a
OL,8,Flight on local visions and voices from
OL,9,Facross the UK, which will encourage
OL,10,Flocal investment, create a lasting
OL,11,Fsense of pride, and open doors to the
OL,12,Farts for everyone."
OL,14,FIn Cumbria and the south of Scotland
OL,15,Fthere have been towns which have
OL,16,Fsubmitted interest to be the next UK
OL,17,FTown of Culture, including Kendal,
OL,18,FKirkby Lonsdale and Kirkcudbright.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
