OL,3,CCarlisle not shortlisted for UK City
OL,4,Cof Culture as city misses out
OL,6,FFor the first time a prize pot of #10
OL,7,Fmillion will be given to the UK City
OL,8,Fof Culture winner and the three best
OL,9,Fshortlisted non-winners will receive
OL,10,F#125,000.
OL,12,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy said:
OL,13,F"For far too long, opportunity has not
OL,14,Fbeen shared equally across the country.
OL,16,F"The UK City of Culture and new UK
OL,17,FTown of Culture competitions recognise
OL,18,Fthe enormous contributions made by
OL,19,Fcommunities all over the UK who are
OL,20,Fall part of the story of who we are as
OL,21,Fa nation."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
